{
  "texts": [
    "The YOLOv3 and YOLOv4-CSP (small) models have the lowest performance.",
    "While these two models give similar results in terms of accuracy, YOLOv4-CSP is better in terms of speed.",
    "Likewise, while YOLOv3-spp and YOLOv4-CSP have similar accuracy results, YOLOv4-CSP also performs faster.",
    "The reason why the YOLOv4-CSP and proposed YOLOv4-CSP models are faster than other models is that they both have CSPNet on their necks and heads.",
    "Considering the all results in the table, the proposed YOLOv4-CSP model exhibits a higher performance than the others in terms of both accuracy and speed."
  ]
}